  <li>
    <p>Five thousand pounds was <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="settled by marriage articles on Mrs. Bennet and the children"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(根据婚约的规定，Bennet太太和孩子们可以获得...)</code></b>.</p>
